data.description: Nestled in the heart of a serene and family-friendly neighborhood, this charming residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that illuminates the spacious living areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  This meticulously maintained home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a spacious converted 2 car garage, perfect for multi-generational living or extra office/entertainment space.There is ample space for your all your family's needs. The open-concept kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash and plenty of storage, making meal preparation easy.  Escape to your private oasis in the master suit ( in which it could fit a California king mattress no problem) complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are generously sized, each have walk-in closets and perfect for family members or guests.  Outside, the backyard offers a tranquil retreat for relaxation and outdoor entertaining. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this space is sure to become your favorite place to unwind on over .2 of an acre!  With a prime location, near educational opportunities like Texas A&M ,transportation access, HEB, Walmart (within 2 miles), investment potential, diverse community and on-going community improvement and growth development-there is so much to love about this place.   The promise of shopping, educational institutions, restaurants, and ongoing development growth can enhance your quality of life by providing convenience, economic opportunities, and a vibrant atmosphere. Commuting is a breeze, thanks to nearby major highways 37 & 281,I-10 and 410.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort that 3818 Killarney Drive has to offer. Your dream home awaits!
